video.title: Ink Master
video.synopsis: Ten of the country's most skilled tattoo artists compete for $100,000 and the title of Ink Master in this high-stakes elimination competition.

episodes.synopsis: A visit to the morgue launches 16 of the best tattoo artists into a brutal competition, and "tattoo virgins" get their first taste of ink.
episodes.title: Tattooing the Dead

episodes.synopsis: Seminude women heat up the competition, and a medical emergency threatens the future of one artist. NFL linebacker Terrell Suggs is a guest judge.
episodes.title: Semi Nude 911

episodes.synopsis: A botched American flag and a backward eagle tattoo cause veterans' patriotic tempers to flare. A third artist falls out of the running for the title.
episodes.title: The 80 Year Old Virgin

episodes.synopsis: A face-off leaves Sarah in tears, and the artists are pushed to their limits when one canvas demands a tattoo on her private parts.
episodes.title: Tattoo Her What?

episodes.synopsis: Halloween gets freaky when the artists tattoo inside mouths. One artist reveals shocking news that lands him in the hospital fighting for his life.
episodes.title: Trick or Freak

episodes.synopsis: Guns and a hot, half-naked pinup model set the stage for one artist's plan for revenge. Some of the artists botch their pinup tattoos.
episodes.title: Half Naked and Fully Loaded

episodes.synopsis: The artists ink critical superfans with "Star Wars" tattoos. "Star Wars" creator George Lucas has a special treat for the Flash Challenge winner.
episodes.title: Star Wars Forever

episodes.synopsis: Alliances are made and betrayed when the artists team up to work in pairs, and one team must ink a priest. Tatu Baby gets a surprise advantage.
episodes.title: Holy Ink

episodes.synopsis: The artists burn designs onto skin-tight chaps worn by smokin' hot cowgirls. The pressure is on when the artists try to tattoo in Nunez's style.
episodes.title: Buck Off

episodes.synopsis: Dave Navarro raises the stakes when he gives the artists his personal guitars to paint for the Flash Challenge. One human canvas can't stop vomiting.
episodes.title: Blowing Chunks

episodes.synopsis: The artists participate in the portrait challenge, which leaves some canvases with unrecognizable family members permanently inked on their skin.
episodes.title: Better Than Words?

episodes.synopsis: The artists lose control when pro-athlete canvases choose them. Tattoo pain has these NFL and mixed martial arts pros on the floor.
episodes.title: The Bigger They Are

episodes.synopsis: America's votes and insane twists are announced, master canvases are revealed, and the judges choose the next Ink Master.
episodes.title: Ink Master Finale
